{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/blog/layout,_N_T_/blog/[slug]/layout,_N_T_/blog/[slug]/page,_N_T_/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--R54jI80Dw697kr80tJYSc--><html lang=\"zh-TW\" class=\"__variable_930adb __variable_833e3a\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/3b891b14d3cf1415-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/604a121a6fa1a135-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/1bf7c22a57b7469d8d47e9ec5ade4473_dfdf0.png\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/e0aad287a7bfe129.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/b13bb92b379b2030.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/51263da16d835ae4.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-f3c1a4c5383f0d5e.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-881ba9d46d833261.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-2b02549a5d25ddac.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/619-ba102abea3e3d0e4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/356-1cbf59d25a49fb83.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/blog/%5Bslug%5D/page-8a1ac09d2c5c1bba.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-54122d456140fd6d.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" sizes=\"any\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#4a5824\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com\"/><link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/hero-grove.webp\" type=\"image/webp\" fetchPriority=\"high\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>IOC 感官評鑑全解析：為什麼一瓶橄欖油的靈魂，藏在鼻尖的三秒鐘？｜知橄生活｜知橄生活 Olive Wisdom</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"國際橄欖油委員會（IOC）的官方感官評鑑方法，要求品油師在 28°C 的藍色杯中，靜靜感受那三秒的香氣爆發。學會這套語言，您將不再被標籤欺騙。\"/><link rel=\"author\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"知橄生活研究團隊\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"橄欖油,特級初榨橄欖油,EVOO,地中海飲食,抗衰老,多酚,羥基酪醇,SIRT1,健康飲食\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"zh-TW\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"x-default\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"IOC 感官評鑑全解析：為什麼一瓶橄欖油的靈魂，藏在鼻尖的三秒鐘？\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"國際橄欖油委員會（IOC）的官方感官評鑑方法，要求品油師在 28°C 的藍色杯中，靜靜感受那三秒的香氣爆發。學會這套語言，您將不再被標籤欺騙。\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"zh_TW\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://bnotescoffee.com/images/ai/evoo-tasting-science.jpg\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"IOC 感官評鑑全解析：為什麼一瓶橄欖油的靈魂，藏在鼻尖的三秒鐘？\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=