"div\",null,{\"className\":\"p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\",\"children\":\"橄欖油真偽鑑別：為什麼歐盟每年查獲數十噸摻假油，而您的舌頭可能是最後一道防線？\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\",\"children\":[9,\" 分鐘閱讀\"]}]]}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L2\",\"olive-oil-terroir-spain-greece-italy\",{\"href\":\"/blog/olive-oil-terroir-spain-greece-italy\",\"className\":\"group\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1c\",null,{\"src\":\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/21efe059834d48fdb33d24f0285fb2de_fe61b.png\",\"alt\":\"橄欖油的風土密碼：為什麼西班牙、希臘與義大利的同種橄欖，能孕育出截然不同的靈魂？ — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"fill\":true,\"className\":\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\",\"unoptimized\":true}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\",\"children\":\"橄欖油的風土密碼：為什麼西班牙、希臘與義大利的同種橄欖，能孕育出截然不同的靈魂？\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\",\"children\":[7,\" 分鐘閱讀\"]}]]}]]}]}]]}]]}]}]\n24:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"💬\"}],\" 常見問題\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"details\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"什麼是橄欖油的 IOC 感官評鑑？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"IOC（國際橄欖理事會）的官方感官評鑑是判定橄欖油等級的法定標準。評鑑在 28°C 的深藍色玻璃杯中進行，以避免顏色干擾判斷。品評師先搖晃杯子後直接嗅聞，評估果香（Fruitiness）強度；接著小口品嘗，評估苦味（Bitterness）和辛辣感（Pungency）。三項正向特徵均需達標，才能被認定為特級初榨橄欖油。\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"橄欖油喝起來嗆喉嚨是好事還是壞事？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"嗆喉嚨是好事。那股喉嚨後部的辛辣刺激感，是橄欖油中 Oleocanthal（油橄欖醛）的標誌性特徵。Oleocanthal 已被科學研究證實具有類似 Ibuprofen 的抗炎機制。品油師以「幾咳」來評估 Oleocanthal 濃度：一咳（單咳）代表含量中等，二至三咳代表頂級多酚濃度。完全沒有嗆感的橄欖油，通常代表多酚含量極低。\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"IOC 認定的橄欖油缺陷味有哪些？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"IOC 感官評鑑定義了多種缺陷味（Defects），常見的包括：Rancid（油耗味）—— 氧化後產生的腐敗味；Fusty（發酵味）—— 橄欖未及時壓榨導致的發酵氣味；Muddy Sediment（泥土味）—— 果渣污染；Winey（酒味/醋味）—— 過度發酵；Metallic（金屬味）—— 接觸金屬設備的汙染。任何一種缺陷的出現，即使輕微，也代表該油無法被評定為特級初榨。\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"我自己在家如何進行簡單的橄欖油品質測試？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"在家可執行三步驟簡易測試：(1) 嗅聞測試：倒少量橄欖油在手掌，雙手摩擦加溫後嗅聞，新鮮高品質油應有綠草、青蕃茄、杏仁或成熟果香；若有油耗、蠟燭、金屬或發酵氣味，代表品質有問題；(2) 吞嚥測試：小口含在嘴中感受苦味，吞下後感受喉嚨刺激感，越強代表多酚越豐富；(3) 包裝檢查：查看採收年份（非僅最佳食用日期）、酸度標示（≤0.8%）和認證標誌。\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n25:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"📚\"}],\" 參考文獻\"]}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\",\"children\":[\"[\",1,\"]\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"International Olive Council (2023). Sensory Analysis of Olive Oil. COI/T.20/Doc. No 15/Rev.13.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\",\"children\":[\"[\",2,\"]\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Aparicio, R. & Harwood, J. (2013). Handbook of Olive Oil. Springer.\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n26:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 flex gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog\",\"className\":\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-olive-600 hover:text-olive-800 font-medium hover:underline\",\"children\":\"← 返回文章列表\"}],[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"href\":\"/#subscribe\",\"className\":\"ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-colors\",\"children\":\"訂閱知橄週報 🫒\"}]]}]\n17:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n13:null\n15:{\"metadata\":[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"IOC 感官評鑑全解析：為什麼一瓶橄欖油的靈魂，藏在鼻尖的三秒鐘？｜知橄生活｜知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"國際橄欖油委員會（IOC）的官方感官評鑑方法，要求品油師在 28°C 的藍色杯中，靜靜感受那三秒的香氣爆發。學會這套語言，您將不再被標籤欺騙。\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"2\",{\"rel\":\"author\",\"href\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"name\":\"author\",\"content\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"name\":\"keywords\",\"content\":\"橄欖油,特級初榨橄欖油,EVOO,地中海飲食,抗衰老,多酚,羥基酪醇,SIRT1,健康飲食\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"name\":\"creator\",\"content\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"name\":\"publisher\",\"content\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"name\":\"robots\",\"content\":\"index, follow\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"8\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"9\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"zh-TW\",\"href\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards/\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"10\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"x-default\",\"href\":\"https://olive-wisdo